Performance Visualizer
========================

Usage
----------------

* Navigate to {ipaddress}:5003 on your browser (e.g. http://172.27.28.31:5003/)
* If you are presented with the following login use admin:admin as user/pass and login

.. image:: ../_static/Grafana-Login.png
    :width: 400
    :alt: First login

* If you are asked for a new password, just press skip on the bottom left to ignore having a password

.. image:: ../_static/Grafana-Pass.png
    :width: 400
    :alt: First login

* You should then be presented with the home page

.. image:: ../_static/Grafana-Home.png
    :width: 400
    :alt: First login

* From here, follow the following short video to navigate through

.. raw:: html

    <video width="800" height="600" controls>
        <source src="../_static/Grafana-dashboard.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    <p>Your browser does not support the video tag.</p>
    </video>

* Once the dashboard is available, you can start running your various tests

Set up after reboot
-----------------------------

Run the following commands manually by sshing into the node in order to restart the dashboard as
well. **Note** these commands are only for nodes that are already set up and have only been rebooted. 

..  code-block:: sh

    sudo docker restart grafana
    sudo docker restart prometheus


